  "title": "QA Engineer (Quality Engineer – Electrical)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li><strong>Well Established Company</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Basic $3200 to $4500 + AWS + VB</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Working Location: Tuas, Singapore</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Company Transport Provided: Boon Lay; Choa Chu Kang; Bukit Batok</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Monday to Friday (8:15am to 5:45pm)</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Develop and implement inspection and testing protocols for incoming and outgoing materials and components.</strong></li>\n  <li>Analyze non-conformities and initiate corrective and preventive actions (CAPA).</li>\n  <li>Liaise with suppliers and subcontractors to resolve quality issues and improve incoming part quality.</li>\n  <li><strong>Conduct root cause analysis for product failures or customer complaints and support resolution efforts.</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Participate in internal quality audits in compliance with ISO or other Quality Management System (QMS) standards.</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Support continuous improvement initiatives to enhance product and process quality.</strong></li>\n  <li>Collaborate with engineering, production, and supply chain teams to ensure quality requirements are met.</li>\n  <li>Maintain Quality Management System documentation, including SOPs, work instructions, and quality reports.</li>\n  <li><strong>Assist in testing and commissioning activities as needed.</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Represent the QA function in project meetings and customer quality reviews as required.</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma / Degree in Electrical Engineering or equivalent</li>\n  <li><strong>Experience in quality assurance or quality engineering roles, preferably in manufacturing or electrical/electronic industries.</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via <strong>Apply Now </strong>button with the following information in the resume:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li>\n  <li>Current and Expected salary</li>\n  <li>Reason for leaving</li>\n  <li>Date of availability</li>\n  <li>Education background</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>NG DIAUM YEE (R2198031)</p>\n<p>EA Recruitment Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
